WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:07.763
It is not proper, but He was not just a mere king, you see.

00:00:07.964 --> 00:00:11.080
He was a Devi bhakta and an ansha avatara

00:00:11.080 --> 00:00:14.056
and his mother was also an ansha avatara.

00:00:14.057 --> 00:00:18.957
What is the sign of an ansha avatara is

00:00:18.957 --> 00:00:24.270
that they have extra powers

00:00:24.269 --> 00:00:26.912
over themselves and over others,

00:00:26.912 --> 00:00:31.677
and they have no temptations, no mistakes.

00:00:31.733 --> 00:00:37.860
[Marathi]

00:00:37.860 --> 00:00:42.460
What's the problem?

00:00:43.479 --> 00:00:47.452
Something wrong with your machinary?

00:00:47.452 --> 00:00:52.968
[Marathi]

00:01:02.522 --> 00:01:07.403
So first of al,l we should know that Shivaji himself

00:01:07.403 --> 00:01:13.573
was a divine person in the sense that He had no defects in him.

00:01:13.573 --> 00:01:17.811
He was a detached personality.

00:01:21.291 --> 00:01:24.585
I do not want to tell you the whole history about him,

00:01:24.584 --> 00:01:26.989
but his character if you study,

00:01:26.989 --> 00:01:30.405
you will be amazed how detached He was.

00:01:30.405 --> 00:01:36.408
He was not found of women. He never hankered after them

00:01:36.408 --> 00:01:41.924
and on the contrary respected women very much.

00:01:41.924 --> 00:01:46.562
There is a story that once He was presented

00:01:46.562 --> 00:01:52.779
with the daughter-in-law of a great nawab,

00:01:52.780 --> 00:02:01.942
because the people used to do,

00:02:01.941 --> 00:02:04.481
I do not know what you call those tactics,

00:02:04.481 --> 00:02:10.143
where you attack the people hiding from behind.

00:02:10.143 --> 00:02:14.135
They used to...

00:02:14.135 --> 00:02:18.806
What's the matter?

00:02:19.020 --> 00:02:22.277
Give the hand there like it.

00:02:22.377 --> 00:02:26.297
As if some plug is missing.

00:03:06.982 --> 00:03:16.102
(...) means that electricity is reduced a little bit at this time,

00:03:16.304 --> 00:03:20.772
on every Tuesday.

00:03:20.973 --> 00:03:24.685
It is a local problem.

00:03:24.886 --> 00:03:29.540
So one has to face it

00:03:29.741 --> 00:03:34.852
I can talk to you, otherwise, can you hear Me?

00:03:34.853 --> 00:03:37.734
Let Me start it, let see what happens.

00:03:37.935 --> 00:03:44.518
Now, please pay attention, you can hear Me from your Sahasrara.

00:03:49.979 --> 00:03:53.829
You pay attention to your Sahasrara, you can hear Me.

00:03:53.829 --> 00:03:57.353
When can I can hear you, you can hear Me, you should be able to.

00:03:57.353 --> 00:04:05.138
Try to do it. Close your eyes and listen to Me in your Sahasrara

00:04:06.709 --> 00:04:11.082
Not through you ears, but through your Sahasrara

00:04:11.082 --> 00:04:13.597
Now, can you hear Me?

00:04:13.798 --> 00:04:18.875
Better try other thing that you have within yourself.

00:04:25.278 --> 00:04:29.444
The inner instrument must be used.

00:04:30.757 --> 00:04:35.201
Can you hear Me now?

00:04:36.353 --> 00:04:39.604
That's why electricity has failed.

00:04:39.805 --> 00:04:46.336
Otherwise you would neve use your
Sahasrara you use your ears only.

00:04:46.336 --> 00:04:51.042
Now try to hear through you Sahasrara.

00:04:51.043 --> 00:04:57.733
You will hear Me very clear if you try to hear Me through your Sahasrara.

00:05:00.454 --> 00:05:03.922
So this great king Shivaji

00:05:03.922 --> 00:05:07.893
was a man without any temptation for women

00:05:07.893 --> 00:05:12.861
and once He was presented with a very beautiful lady

00:05:12.862 --> 00:05:15.762
who was the daughter-in-law of a big nawab,

00:05:15.817 --> 00:05:22.468
because they looted lot of money and lot of precious things

00:05:22.669 --> 00:05:27.860
and this lady as well when her caravan was passing through

00:05:27.860 --> 00:05:36.300
some passage in the mountains.

00:05:36.300 --> 00:05:41.000
So Shivaji looked at her.

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:45.938
He asked her to remover her veil because she was a Muslim lady

00:05:45.938 --> 00:05:49.529
and then looking at her He said that

00:05:49.529 --> 00:05:55.624
"if my mother was as beautiful as you
are, I would have been equally beautiful",

00:05:55.624 --> 00:05:59.587
is the best way to say "you are my sister."

00:05:59.587 --> 00:06:02.587
He himself had to marry four times,

00:06:02.587 --> 00:06:09.487
because of certain problems of political nature,

00:06:09.487 --> 00:06:13.812
where He had to marry four women, but He married them,

00:06:13.813 --> 00:06:18.126
because He had to marry and all the four wives were his wives

00:06:18.126 --> 00:06:21.070
and no other women came into his head.

00:06:21.070 --> 00:06:23.764
This is such a tremendous character.

00:06:23.764 --> 00:06:28.891
This is first sign of a personality who is really mature,

00:06:28.891 --> 00:06:32.656
who has no attention towards another women,

00:06:32.656 --> 00:06:36.751
which is very common, in Maharasthra it is not difficult for them,

00:06:36.751 --> 00:06:40.675
they do not understand what I am talking about.

00:06:40.675 --> 00:06:43.096
This is one of the things one has to understand

00:06:43.096 --> 00:06:46.334
how respectful He was to other women.

00:06:46.334 --> 00:06:50.558
That He gave away all her things, all her money, all her jewelry,

00:06:50.726 --> 00:06:56.020
all that was looted of that nawab also, all the arms, everything,

00:06:56.020 --> 00:07:00.896
and sent back all the people to the nawab,

00:07:00.896 --> 00:07:05.249
because if there is a lady, she is the shakti, she is traveling,

00:07:05.249 --> 00:07:10.186
so nobody has business to trouble her.

00:07:10.185 --> 00:07:14.291
This was his respect for women who belonged actually

00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:18.934
to another party.

00:07:20.403 --> 00:07:24.057
He had so many qualities that it is impossible to describe all that,

00:07:24.057 --> 00:07:33.520
but absolutely honest, absolutely honest He was and He lived like a saint.

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:35.520
He did not care for comfort.

00:07:35.742 --> 00:07:41.348
If you go and see his things that the had, you will be amazed,

00:07:41.349 --> 00:07:44.992
He could sleep on the stones,

00:07:44.992 --> 00:07:50.551
but for his kingship, He had to wear all the ornaments,

00:07:50.550 --> 00:07:54.479
all the dresses which He used to wear.

00:07:54.479 --> 00:07:59.200
If you go in Bombay museum, you will see chilkhat

00:07:59.200 --> 00:08:07.065
we call it a cover made out of iron mesh.

00:08:07.065 --> 00:08:11.878
He used to wear that, it is so heavy that you cannot lift it,

00:08:11.877 --> 00:08:18.155
but He had to wear it and He used to fight his wars wearing that,

00:08:18.155 --> 00:08:20.571
but like all other kings you see in the west,

00:08:20.571 --> 00:08:26.571
He didn't have weaknesses,
he had no weakness, he had no habits,

00:08:26.571 --> 00:08:32.765
extremely honest, Spartan in temperament,

00:08:32.765 --> 00:08:40.094
and absolute ideal king He was, an absolute ideal king.

00:08:40.093 --> 00:08:47.026
He talked to everyone on the same
level, treated everybody with respect,

00:08:47.025 --> 00:08:51.041
never showed off that he was a king, but He kept his dignity

00:08:51.041 --> 00:08:53.997
all the time and when it was needed to be corrected,

00:08:53.997 --> 00:08:57.240
with all courage He corrected people, He did not care for

00:08:57.240 --> 00:09:02.100
cheap popularity either.

00:09:02.100 --> 00:09:05.659
Such a man was a blessing to Maharashtra.

00:09:05.659 --> 00:09:12.083
because He is such an ideal for us and for people to follow

00:09:12.083 --> 00:09:19.991
and His mother was a great lady who brought
him out of the clutches of the Mughal people

00:09:19.991 --> 00:09:27.221
who tried to convert forcibly Hindus to Islam.

00:09:27.221 --> 00:09:33.716
Like this Aurangzeb, he used to hate music, and he would kill,

00:09:33.716 --> 00:09:38.322
very right sided fellow, every year the brahmins,

00:09:38.323 --> 00:09:42.236
so many brahmins that the thread they used to wear

00:09:42.235 --> 00:09:45.933
should weigh according to his body, body weight.

00:09:45.934 --> 00:09:50.622
So you can imagine what a cruel man he was. He was like Hitler only,

00:09:50.622 --> 00:09:54.160
but he was also very honest in the sense he used to make

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:58.617
his own caps and sell them and live on that money.

00:09:58.617 --> 00:10:02.200
He was very right sided who was honest as far as the money was concerned,

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:04.600
the government money was concerned,

00:10:04.625 --> 00:10:13.295
but he was so fanatically imprisoned in his own ideas about God

00:10:13.295 --> 00:10:18.179
that he had become just like a rakshasa.

00:10:18.179 --> 00:10:20.362
To face him was very difficult in those days,

00:10:20.563 --> 00:10:24.960
he was a terror. Nobody could face Hitler from inside

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:30.087
but Shivaji managed it and he did it so well.

00:10:30.087 --> 00:10:35.471
So Satara is a place where he established his first kingdom.

00:10:35.471 --> 00:10:42.681
This is the capital of Maharashtra, Satara,
that is why it is a very important place.

00:10:42.681 --> 00:10:48.276
Secondly, after Shivaji, or when Shivaji was the king

00:10:48.276 --> 00:10:50.533
looking after the whole worldly affairs,

00:10:50.533 --> 00:10:54.255
his own son fell into a bad company of a fellow

00:10:54.255 --> 00:10:58.425
who came from Uttar Pradesh called Kabji Kalusha,

00:10:58.426 --> 00:11:02.513
who started drinking and doing all wrong things

00:11:02.513 --> 00:11:06.667
that should not be done. He was imprisoned,

00:11:06.667 --> 00:11:13.680
but even then he was a very-very lost case,

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:18.291
but a good hearted fellow

00:11:18.291 --> 00:11:23.762
that is why this Maharasthra was divided into two

00:11:23.762 --> 00:11:28.635
and his younger brother had to form another kingdom

00:11:28.635 --> 00:11:34.186
or another part of the capital was in Kohlapur,

00:11:34.186 --> 00:11:41.154
where you saw Sambaji, I think you
have seen Sahu Maharaja’s statue there.

00:11:41.154 --> 00:11:45.947
So he was a very dharmic fellow, very good person

00:11:45.947 --> 00:11:49.495
and he looked after that part very well.

00:11:49.494 --> 00:11:55.510
So Kohlapur started another capital, but what I am trying to say

00:11:55.711 --> 00:12:01.041
that when negativity starts crawling into something great,

00:12:01.041 --> 00:12:03.636
then it starts getting divided

00:12:03.636 --> 00:12:06.652
and it is now a very common character, they say, of Marathas,

00:12:06.652 --> 00:12:10.108
that they indulge in Bhau Bandki, always form groups.

00:12:10.298 --> 00:12:13.909
I find it even happening in Sahaja Yoga. I went to Rahuri,

00:12:13.909 --> 00:12:18.730
I felt that in Rahuri also there is a kind of Bhau Bandki working out.

00:12:18.730 --> 00:12:22.441
This is character of Marathas and they have to be very-very careful about it.

00:12:22.642 --> 00:12:26.223
One of them is Bhau Bandki
that they form a group suddenly

00:12:26.424 --> 00:12:31.471
and separate themselves from one another and start fighting each other,

00:12:31.471 --> 00:12:37.355
it is sort of a coagulation that takes place in their temperaments.

00:12:37.355 --> 00:12:41.358
One must understand that unless and until absolutely we are united,

00:12:41.358 --> 00:12:43.358
we cannot do Sahaja Yoga.

00:12:43.559 --> 00:12:46.787
So this kind of separation is a very wrong thing

00:12:46.787 --> 00:12:50.731
which should be avoided out and out

00:12:50.932 --> 00:12:54.996
and one thing I want to tell all the Maharashtrians

00:12:54.997 --> 00:12:58.302
that they have to be careful on this point is Bhau Bandki.

00:12:58.301 --> 00:13:06.106
his comes out of jealousy, out of thirst for power,

00:13:06.106 --> 00:13:11.765
for not accepting somebody as the leader,
trying to find faults all the time.

00:13:11.765 --> 00:13:15.887
If the leader is wrong also it can happen. If the leader goes wrong,

00:13:15.887 --> 00:13:19.887
if he is not a person who can carry on well with others

00:13:19.887 --> 00:13:24.034
and something, it can happen. So it is quite a mutual thing that works out

00:13:24.235 --> 00:13:27.592
but as a result of the whole thing is that

00:13:27.793 --> 00:13:31.431
it starts getting bifurcated and that is how we lost

00:13:31.632 --> 00:13:37.013
the kingdom of Maharasthra ultimately.

00:13:37.822 --> 00:13:41.444
So it’s a very good example of understanding

00:13:41.445 --> 00:13:45.770
how Shivaji worked hard, fought Aurangzeb,

00:13:45.770 --> 00:13:49.592
established his kingdom and how it was lost

00:13:49.793 --> 00:13:53.603
in second generation itself. [TN:Talk continues]

00:13:53.804 --> 00:13:58.609
I was telling about Shivaji Maharaj because he had established Satara as the capital.

00:13:58.810 --> 00:14:04.058
We must adopt the qualities that he possessed.

00:14:04.259 --> 00:14:06.874
The special trait about him was that he had no faults,

00:14:07.075 --> 00:14:10.105
that we have as a human being, like

00:14:10.306 --> 00:14:13.092
someone has bad habit, someone has addiction,

00:14:13.092 --> 00:14:16.505
someone's is crazy about and runs after somebody.

00:14:16.706 --> 00:14:21.592
This proves that he was an anshavatar. As he was an anshavatar,

00:14:21.793 --> 00:14:25.401
he didn't have any bad habit like lieing, drinking alcohol etc.

00:14:25.401 --> 00:14:28.401
Was not needed to tell him. He was simply not like that.

00:14:28.655 --> 00:14:32.215
Second, his temperament was very sweet, he was very sweet.

00:14:32.416 --> 00:14:37.972
Extremely sweet and totally surrendered to his mother.

00:14:38.173 --> 00:14:42.173
He never uttered a bad word to anyone or shouted at anyone,

00:14:42.374 --> 00:14:46.253
or got angry with anyone. These two qualities are very difficult to find.

00:14:46.454 --> 00:14:51.264
When a person has such a great mother's blessing

00:14:51.465 --> 00:14:57.523
and even more importance this blessing gets, because he was a king.

00:14:57.724 --> 00:15:02.870
But still he was very sweet in nature.

00:15:03.071 --> 00:15:06.262
He didn´t think too highly of himself saying, 'I am a king.

00:15:06.463 --> 00:15:09.984
They are poor or they are mawlas. How can I talk to them?

00:15:10.185 --> 00:15:13.022
He used to sit with them, take food with them.

00:15:13.223 --> 00:15:15.336
He was having fun to eat onion and bhakri (maharashtrian Millet bread) with them.

00:15:15.537 --> 00:15:19.743
Night and day he used to travel riding
on his horse, sleep anywhere at night.

00:15:19.944 --> 00:15:22.714
do anything. That is how he spent his life.

00:15:22.915 --> 00:15:26.954
He had very gruelling, hard working life and he suffered a lot.

00:15:27.204 --> 00:15:30.204
After that, when Sambhaji Maharaj and Shahu Maharaj (his two sons)

00:15:30.204 --> 00:15:33.473
got into a dispute, the only reason for that was sibling rivalry.

00:15:33.674 --> 00:15:36.402
It is the nature of our Marathas.

00:15:36.603 --> 00:15:40.490
This is very deep conditioning inside us without which we can't do anything,

00:15:40.691 --> 00:15:44.364
But we are not ready to accept that we have sibling rivalry in us.

00:15:44.565 --> 00:15:46.652
We are not ready to listen to this thing,

00:15:46.853 --> 00:15:49.323
But this is very deep rooted in us. So be aware of it!

00:15:49.524 --> 00:15:51.564
I observe this one-upmanship even in Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:51.814 --> 00:15:54.109
It's everywhere, wherever we go.

00:15:54.310 --> 00:15:56.874
This is one of the shortcomings in Maharashtra.

00:15:57.075 --> 00:16:00.074
We lost a kingdom because of this sibling rivalry,

00:16:00.275 --> 00:16:03.673
due to which now we should not lose the kingdom of God anymore.

00:16:03.874 --> 00:16:07.124
People who are doing God´s work should be kept together,

00:16:07.325 --> 00:16:09.870
should not break anyone. Don't speak harsh to others.

00:16:10.071 --> 00:16:13.149
This was not Shivaji Maharaj´s style.

00:16:13.350 --> 00:16:16.882
He always gave importance to those who did some work.

00:16:17.083 --> 00:16:20.402
You know, when he got a Sinhgad,

00:16:20.402 --> 00:16:25.219
he said, 'We won the fort but lost the lion´. That's a very big deal.

00:16:25.420 --> 00:16:29.152
`What if we got a fort, but we lost a brave warrior!´

00:16:29.353 --> 00:16:33.493
And from his behavior, we all have to learn that

00:16:33.694 --> 00:16:37.754
also in Sahaja Yoga it is very important to value another person.

00:16:37.955 --> 00:16:39.997
Do not praise only yourself.

00:16:40.198 --> 00:16:43.386
"I'm special, I'm particular, I'm everything. Don't do this."

00:16:43.587 --> 00:16:45.401
Many people think that they are educated.

00:16:45.401 --> 00:16:48.199
In Sahaja Yoga many people are comfortably well off and educated.

00:16:48.400 --> 00:16:51.255
So they don't mix with people with less privilaged section of society.

00:16:51.456 --> 00:16:53.634
This is wrong. They are different from us, we are different,

00:16:53.834 --> 00:16:55.789
They should live separate we should stay apart from them.

00:16:55.990 --> 00:16:58.704
If you feel that way, then you haven´t yet understood Sahaja Yoga.

00:16:58.905 --> 00:17:02.914
Yogies don't have cast or creed, high or low class mentality at all.

00:17:02.914 --> 00:17:06.827
Sahaja Yogis should not even differenciate on basis of rich and poor.

00:17:07.028 --> 00:17:09.057
Only then you will be a yogy.

00:17:09.258 --> 00:17:13.104
So, the identity of the yogies is that we are all one.

00:17:13.305 --> 00:17:17.124
We are all children of one mother. There should be no difference between us.

00:17:17.124 --> 00:17:22.073
There should be equality in us.
If we want to change our country,

00:17:22.097 --> 00:17:27.830
as we have seen an example of Shivaji,

00:17:28.031 --> 00:17:31.781
there should be no flaws in ourselves.

00:17:31.982 --> 00:17:35.473
If a person has his own flaws, what will he be able to preach others?

00:17:35.674 --> 00:17:40.842
Secondly, those who followed him had an immense faith in him.

00:17:41.043 --> 00:17:45.283
It is wrong all the time just to argue with and find faults in your leaders.

00:17:45.283 --> 00:17:48.591
If both things are reconciled, then only sibling rivalry won´t exist.

00:17:48.792 --> 00:17:55.943
But if not, then the rivalry thrives. It is very wrong to talk harsh.

00:17:55.949 --> 00:17:59.724
But it is also wrong not to respect your leader,

00:17:59.925 --> 00:18:06.603
constantly to humiliate him, to correct him as such, to teach him.

00:18:06.804 --> 00:18:09.445
So if we manage these two things

00:18:09.646 --> 00:18:13.154
then sibling rivalry in our country will end.

00:18:13.355 --> 00:18:15.845
It must vanish. It should be uprooted completely.

00:18:16.058 --> 00:18:20.332
It won´t work looking at other's faults, first try to remove faults from yourself.

00:18:20.533 --> 00:18:26.114
I am speaking this in satara as in Satara only Swarajya was established

00:18:26.315 --> 00:18:31.341
and in Satara only its disintegration began.

00:18:31.542 --> 00:18:33.792
So both things must be kept in mind.

00:18:33.993 --> 00:18:37.178
There should be no anarchic behaviur within us. This is the act of love.

00:18:37.379 --> 00:18:39.435
We should conect people through love.

00:18:39.636 --> 00:18:43.525
Whatever other ideas and all the stuff people do, like some are intellectuals

00:18:43.726 --> 00:18:46.502
and so they get away from others.

00:18:46.703 --> 00:18:49.986
You should live on the power of love.

00:18:50.187 --> 00:18:54.985
Love is the food of Sahaja Yoga. We need
to see, how much do we love others?

00:18:54.985 --> 00:19:00.482
how much we give to others, rather than find faults in them.

00:19:00.885 --> 00:19:04.459
Thats why both things should be used with care.

00:19:04.660 --> 00:19:08.434
I'm so happy that this work now started in Satara.

00:19:08.635 --> 00:19:10.440
I felt very nice yesterday.

00:19:10.641 --> 00:19:14.193
Lots of seekers were there and many got their realisation. In Sahaja Yoga,

00:19:14.394 --> 00:19:17.407
grand work is to be done and many will achieve great heights,

00:19:17.608 --> 00:19:20.605
Those sitting here are the leaders of the future.

00:19:20.806 --> 00:19:24.600
So it was very pleasing to me. But we should keep in mind

00:19:24.801 --> 00:19:27.838
that whatever mistakes were made earlier in politics

00:19:28.039 --> 00:19:32.965
should not be comitted again in the kingdom of God.

00:19:32.965 --> 00:19:36.781
The laws of the God's Kingdom are very strong and very strict.

00:19:36.982 --> 00:19:40.355
The person who goes against that law is straight away punished.

00:19:40.556 --> 00:19:44.120
We should be careful. Very careful.

00:19:44.321 --> 00:19:52.200
His blessings and forgiveness are immense, but up to a limit.

00:19:52.401 --> 00:19:57.224
After that, his rath is severe. Then you won´t be able to do anything.

00:19:57.425 --> 00:20:01.870
So remember, now we are entering into the kingdom of the God,

00:20:02.071 --> 00:20:06.298
So we should keep this wisdom not to bring

00:20:06.499 --> 00:20:11.785
wretched politics of any kind here. Don't bring this dirty thing here.

00:20:11.785 --> 00:20:15.685
In this kingdom of love, we all are tied to each other by the same cord.

00:20:15.886 --> 00:20:18.797
We are the children of the same mother. So the power we need

00:20:18.998 --> 00:20:21.956
to attain should not be forced on others. Instead, apply it on your ownself.

00:20:22.157 --> 00:20:24.495
This is not a place to rule on others.

00:20:24.495 --> 00:20:27.902
One must understand that this is the place to get mastery on yourself.

00:20:28.103 --> 00:20:30.442
If you gain that mastery, first thing,

00:20:30.643 --> 00:20:33.104
it will manifest in your vibrations.

00:20:33.305 --> 00:20:37.217
According to your vibrations, I can understand what is going on inside you.

00:20:37.418 --> 00:20:39.904
How it is going and where it's going haywire.

00:20:40.105 --> 00:20:43.652
So please don´t practice any type of sibling rivalry or form groups,

00:20:43.652 --> 00:20:46.054
and if done, break them.

00:20:46.255 --> 00:20:49.765
"Mataji told, not to split in groups, not to talk against anyone.

00:20:50.003 --> 00:20:55.485
nor talk ill of anybody. Don't create
groups. Everyone should stay together."

00:20:55.686 --> 00:21:00.099
The thought came to me at Satara, to make the people

00:21:00.300 --> 00:21:05.966
here now aware of it. Because Sahaja Yoga is very easy to get.

00:21:06.167 --> 00:21:11.645
And the first thing that happenes that one gets power,

00:21:11.846 --> 00:21:14.066
and with that, one tends to overpower others.

00:21:14.267 --> 00:21:20.542
Or others say, 'Why does this man do so much?

00:21:20.743 --> 00:21:22.748
That is also wrong.

00:21:22.949 --> 00:21:26.121
If one tries to supress others, people think, who is he to do this?

00:21:26.322 --> 00:21:30.335
So in Sahaja Yoga you should keep in mind that Mataji has appointed

00:21:30.335 --> 00:21:36.634
one person everywhere. And She
has communication with everyone.

00:21:36.835 --> 00:21:40.395
Through that appointment only She communicates.

00:21:40.596 --> 00:21:45.339
Just like we have a brain in our head that communicates with the whole body.

00:21:45.540 --> 00:21:48.016
Same is to be done in Sahaja Yoga.

00:21:48.217 --> 00:21:50.920
So if anything goes wrong with that person,

00:21:50.920 --> 00:21:53.146
I will notice it right away, I can fix him.

00:21:53.347 --> 00:21:57.584
But if you try to find faults in him, you will ruin everything.

00:21:57.785 --> 00:22:04.305
Isn´t it, did you get the point?
Accept a person who is your leader.

00:22:04.506 --> 00:22:10.814
I will keep an eye on him. If he makes a
mistake, I will know everything, of everyone.

00:22:11.015 --> 00:22:15.015
You don't know how well I know this. Because I don't tell you,

00:22:15.015 --> 00:22:17.965
that doesn't mean I don't know. I know everybody.

00:22:17.965 --> 00:22:22.831
When we choose one person as a leader, he must be accepted.

00:22:23.032 --> 00:22:25.961
Trust your Mataji, She will do the right.

00:22:25.961 --> 00:22:29.621
You may be more educated, or you may have more money,

00:22:29.621 --> 00:22:31.734
or whatever you have, but don´t do anything.

00:22:31.935 --> 00:22:36.569
As long as I am okay with that person, accept him as your leader.

00:22:36.770 --> 00:22:41.548
Later on, if he does something wrong, I´ll remove him.

00:22:42.530 --> 00:22:44.930
Keep this in mind that I myself know everything.

00:22:45.131 --> 00:22:53.706
Then Sahaja Yoga is going to increase.
As Sahaja Yoga has no organization,

00:22:53.907 --> 00:22:57.384
You don't have to pay anything, there is no membership,

00:22:57.585 --> 00:23:04.065
then how will we be bonded? Through love.
Everyone should get connected with love.

00:23:04.266 --> 00:23:08.938
And second thing is that the power of love comes from Mataji.

00:23:09.139 --> 00:23:13.497
So believe in the person She chose as a leader, accept him.

00:23:13.698 --> 00:23:17.902
And if I see anything wrong in him, I will take him out.

00:23:18.103 --> 00:23:23.243
I will definately remove him. So you need to completely rely on me.

00:23:23.444 --> 00:23:28.519
How to develope
our character?

00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:34.211
How should we act? To learn this, I'm right in front of you.

00:23:34.412 --> 00:23:39.131
If you think that we cannot be like Mataji, then look at Shivaji Maharaj.

00:23:39.332 --> 00:23:41.521
We have so many people as examples.

00:23:41.521 --> 00:23:43.921
Nothing is too difficult for those who have realisation in Sahaja Yoga.

00:23:43.921 --> 00:23:47.321
Life simply changes. Look at how much these people have changed.

00:23:47.671 --> 00:23:50.420
they couldn't even sit on the ground for five minutes.

00:23:50.621 --> 00:23:54.543
By hard work they learned to sit on the ground.

00:23:56.703 --> 00:23:59.579
So meditation should be done properly.

00:23:59.780 --> 00:24:02.171
Every evening if you meditate at least

00:24:02.372 --> 00:24:06.932
fifteen to twenty minutes before going to sleep it helps to improve.

00:24:06.932 --> 00:24:12.842
And before going outside, or after the morning bath, if you do puja

00:24:12.842 --> 00:24:14.897
to the photo just for five minutes, it will do.

00:24:14.897 --> 00:24:17.892
But all should meet every week.

00:24:17.892 --> 00:24:20.671
If that is not the case, Sahaja Yoga simply doesn't work.

00:24:20.872 --> 00:24:25.642
Everyone should meet every week. Because this is collective consciousness.

00:24:25.843 --> 00:24:29.393
If you say, "Mataji we kept a photo at home, we worship you at home.

00:24:29.602 --> 00:24:32.095
But still we have this problem." My attention doesn´t go there.

00:24:32.296 --> 00:24:38.652
I told you yesterday, that when we whip buttermilk, the butter comes out.

00:24:38.652 --> 00:24:42.312
We take out that sticks to the big lump and the rest all is thrown away.

00:24:42.312 --> 00:24:45.834
Similarly people who cling to the colectivity come to me.

00:24:46.035 --> 00:24:48.046
The rest are not in my attention.

00:24:48.247 --> 00:24:50.917
Then you must go to the place where others meet.

00:24:51.118 --> 00:24:54.461
There you may talk to people, may discuss. But don´t do groupism.

00:24:54.662 --> 00:24:57.645
It will be better to talk less and meditate more.

00:24:57.846 --> 00:25:00.438
If there is groupism, or like, I will heal you, I will fix you,

00:25:00.639 --> 00:25:02.272
I´ll put you in your place…

00:25:02.472 --> 00:25:05.433
If this kind of things start then you are a gone case.

00:25:05.634 --> 00:25:09.632
Everyone must go there and meditate, sing bhajans, do Aarti.

00:25:09.632 --> 00:25:12.302
If you have any issues, sort them out.

00:25:12.503 --> 00:25:18.630
But just sitting there don´t argue with each other or do stupid things.

00:25:18.831 --> 00:25:25.382
Instead, focus on what you want to gain in Sahaja Yoga,

00:25:25.382 --> 00:25:30.009
What about our growth? How much we have grown in sahaj yoga? Where have we reached?

00:25:30.210 --> 00:25:34.543
I think,slowly sahaj yoga will settle in Maharashtra.

00:25:34.543 --> 00:25:37.242
But sometimes I get worried about future,

00:25:37.442 --> 00:25:42.661
that my hard work should not be wasted.

00:25:43.066 --> 00:25:47.162
It is important to remember that the responsibility of the whole world lies on you.

00:25:47.363 --> 00:25:50.152
The responsibility of the entire world is on Maharashtrians.

00:25:50.152 --> 00:25:55.903
It should be kept in mind. And if you make it lose

00:25:56.104 --> 00:25:58.502
which is also posible for you. So don´t do that.

00:25:58.752 --> 00:26:02.968
Whatever faults are in us must be removed.

00:26:03.169 --> 00:26:07.062
Develope sweetness in your nature. You must talk with love with others.

00:26:07.062 --> 00:26:10.762
Everyone should be treated equaly.

00:26:10.862 --> 00:26:14.112
If this is done outside(in behavior), it will reflect inside.

00:26:14.112 --> 00:26:16.251
Because now, inside out you have become the same.

00:26:16.452 --> 00:26:18.413
Whatever you do outside, will impact inside.

00:26:18.614 --> 00:26:20.521
Whatever you change inside will manifest outside.

00:26:20.722 --> 00:26:23.198
Because inside out you became the same. This doesn´t happen normaly

00:26:23.399 --> 00:26:25.883
but now your conection is established.

00:26:26.084 --> 00:26:28.834
Now if this is defective outside, there is no sound

00:26:29.097 --> 00:26:31.300
and if there is damage from inside still no sound will be there.

00:26:31.501 --> 00:26:33.496
Both things should be in order.

00:26:33.697 --> 00:26:36.782
Many people say that we meditate, Mataji, our vibrations are ok.

00:26:36.782 --> 00:26:38.932
But it should manifest outside too.

00:26:39.149 --> 00:26:41.988
Otherwise, whatever is inside will eventually disappear.

00:26:42.189 --> 00:26:46.797
Therefore, one must be same both inside and outside.

00:26:46.998 --> 00:26:50.154
And should look radient.

00:26:50.355 --> 00:26:53.617
But there should not be any scorching in that radiance.

00:26:53.818 --> 00:26:57.316
The personality should not be agressive.

00:26:57.517 --> 00:27:02.608
But it should be very mild, beautiful and cool, like the moon.

00:27:03.495 --> 00:27:06.745
Next time when I come here, hope there will be more people.

00:27:06.946 --> 00:27:10.815
And we will celebrate a puja all together.

00:27:11.016 --> 00:27:14.742
But this time I will not come. I will come next year.

00:27:14.912 --> 00:27:17.235
This time I will probably stay here for one night.

00:27:17.436 --> 00:27:22.349
So, let's see if we can do something if possible.
